@startuml
!define AZURE_COLOR #0072C6
!define ONPREM_COLOR #808080

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor AZURE_COLOR
    BorderColor AZURE_COLOR
}

participant "Azure Portal" as Portal
participant "Azure Migrate" as Migrate
participant "Azure VM" as VM
participant "Azure Functions" as Functions
participant "Cosmos DB" as CosmosDB
participant "Azure Storage" as Storage
participant "Azure Monitor" as Monitor
participant "Log Analytics" as LogAnalytics
participant "Application Insights" as AppInsights

participant "On-Premises Hyper-V" as HyperV #ONPREM_COLOR

Portal -> Migrate: Create Azure Migrate project
Migrate -> HyperV: Assess on-premises VMs
HyperV --> Migrate: VM assessment data
Migrate -> VM: Replicate servers
Migrate -> VM: Perform test migration
Portal -> VM: Validate migrated servers

Portal -> VM: Create virtual network
Portal -> VM: Configure availability set
Portal -> VM: Deploy VMs
Portal -> VM: Manage data disks
Portal -> VM: Configure VM connectivity
VM -> VM: Install IIS

Portal -> Functions: Publish Azure Functions
Functions -> CosmosDB: Store/retrieve data
Portal -> Storage: Deploy Blazor website
Storage -> Functions: API requests

Monitor -> VM: Collect metrics and logs
Monitor -> Functions: Collect metrics and logs
Monitor -> CosmosDB: Collect metrics and logs
Monitor -> Storage: Collect metrics and logs

Monitor -> LogAnalytics: Send log data
Monitor -> AppInsights: Send application telemetry

Portal -> Monitor: View dashboards and alerts
Portal -> LogAnalytics: Query log data
Portal -> AppInsights: Analyze application performance
@enduml